        "shortName": "G* GFR-X",
        "description": "The GFR-X carries the Geissele Freedom Rifle® pedigree into 5.56x45mm NATO, pairing the platform's fully ambidextrous controls and match-grade fire control group with the ubiquity and light recoil of the world's most common intermediate cartridge. Built for shooters who want GFR® handling and reliability without stepping up to 6mm ARC, it is equally at home as a duty carbine, a home-defense rifle, or a high-volume trainer."
